<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>فَإِن كَانَ فَالضَّمَان وَالْقصاص عَلَيْهِمَا<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
